$$
a^2+b^2 = a^2+2ab+b^2-2ab
$$
[[Completing the square]] gives:
$$
(a+b)^2-2ab=(a+b)^2-(\sqrt{2ab})^2.
$$
Proceed by [[factoring the difference of the two squares|Factoring the difference of two squares]].